{"tid":2352163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實 我覺得美國起碼有三成人中過招","createTime":"2021-01-03T22:06:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T00:04:48.000Z","uid":205928,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0992f2cb45124c0dcb37263fc447cb13730e88b3","tid":2352163,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T22:06:18.000Z","msg":"目前確診二千萬 美國總人口3.282億<br />\n計返姐係6%人口確診<br />\n<br />\n事實上我作為加州居民見過好多中左病完好返都唔敢同人講，又有人輕症到冇味覺一兩日之後有返就當冇事，可能仲有好多好多好多無症狀感染者。<br />\n<br />\n呢度啲人既個性有病又去檢測既真係冇乜幾個，我估計有症狀既人入面應該得30% maybe lesser會去檢測，再加埋無症狀條數真係唔知點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nStudies show that at least 40-to-50% of people who test positive for COVID-19 have no symptoms."},{"pid":"6bc823ad906453d1275a0d1ad3595f7423dd71a5","tid":2352163,"uid":205928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T22:07:37.000Z","msg":"Most people will have mild symptoms and get better on their own. But about 1 in 6 will have severe problems, such as trouble breathing."},{"pid":"efd4be814e7c8d5ca448169dddca086928caedf8","tid":2352163,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T22:09:40.000Z","msg":"點止咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093c87f5c40bb5c87ef7a12394ea326c8b162444","tid":2352163,"uid":332565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T22:11:22.000Z","msg":"My friend tested positive and it took her a week to test negative and I don&rsquo;t think she stayed at a hospital. No doubt there are people who get better on their own and I&rsquo;m not sure how many people can get thru it without getting tested."},{"pid":"65856bf4974dcdf714b647980127fb6ec1b0130c","tid":2352163,"uid":181557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T22:12:43.000Z","msg":"咁又點？"},{"pid":"2fcb2517f36133c006fb527cec3f578aab9ceab1","tid":2352163,"u